{"tid":2043734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PS5 官方確認6月4日發佈會　香港發佈時間 + 首發遊戲","createTime":"2020-05-30T15:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T15:40:41.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c49172f67e58c79cd2f2019dfe02e38ea2757b5","tid":2043734,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ps5tunein_featured_1.0-1280x853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fps5tunein_featured_1.0-1280x853.jpg&h=6a5649e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然對家 Xbox Series X 早在月初舉辦了發佈會，Sony 的 PS5 仍然只有手掣設計和部分硬件細節，令機迷相當焦躁。最近 Sony 終於公佈了 PS5 的發佈會日期，到 6 月 4 日就可以知道更多細節。<br />\n<br />\nSony 今次發佈會的主題為「The Future of Gaming」，將會在 6 月 4 日美國東岸時間下午 4 點（香港時間 6 月 5 日清晨 4 點）正式舉行，長度約 1 小時左右，屆時會分享伴隨 PS5 推出的首發遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nSony Interactive Entertainment 總裁 Jim Ryan 表示，將在 PS5 平台推出的遊戲，會是業界的最佳傑作，來自世界各地的創新遊戲廠商，不論大型小型、新創還是已有豐富經驗的廠商都盡力發揮這個主機的潛能。他更形容，這個網上發佈會上，將會首次讓觀衆一起虛擬感受刺激的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n不過有消息預計，這次發佈會仍然不會公佈所有的細節，將只會是一系列發佈會的其中一個，就連主機設計也不一定會在 6 月 4 日的發佈會上公開。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Verge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15-7tBKVPBA&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D15-7tBKVPBA%26feature%3Demb_title&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=ba733b60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15-7tBKVPBA&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"a148de0b72a3a557ec3036165860cee9415bbd17","tid":2043734,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"毋忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2d61db997d147b71dc7ef1534ec43d01196246","tid":2043734,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"索尼損害我国人民感情<br />\n罪大惡極 罷玩PS5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db963ddf6dda71e259071144589cf70d8251f33","tid":2043734,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"反正香港而家咁樣都冇得首發啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e7cfd3686d1b4fbbcdd4cc35db0fd96a64413e","tid":2043734,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"有人冇機打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}